---
// Sección Especialidades
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 dark:bg-[#0a0a0a]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p
        class="text-xs font-semibold text-[#000000]/60 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase mb-4"
      >
        SERVICIOS QUE OFREZCO
      </p>
      <h2
        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-[#000000] dark:text-white"
      >
        ESPECIALIDADES
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <!-- Card: Bodas -->
      <div
        class="group p-8 border border-[#000000]/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-xl hover:border-[#000000]/30 dark:hover:border-white/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-4">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center bg-[#000000] dark:bg-white rounded-full transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8 text-white dark:text-[#000000]"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#000000] dark:text-white">
            BODAS
          </h3>
          <p
            class="text-sm text-[#000000]/70 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed"
          >
            Cada historia de amor merece ser contada con autenticidad y emoción.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card: Retratos -->
      <div
        class="group p-8 border border-[#000000]/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-xl hover:border-[#000000]/30 dark:hover:border-white/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-4">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center bg-[#000000] dark:bg-white rounded-full transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8 text-white dark:text-[#000000]"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#000000] dark:text-white">
            RETRATOS
          </h3>
          <p
            class="text-sm text-[#000000]/70 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed"
          >
            Capturo la personalidad y esencia única de cada individuo.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card: Eventos -->
      <div
        class="group p-8 border border-[#000000]/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-xl hover:border-[#000000]/30 dark:hover:border-white/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-4">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center bg-[#000000] dark:bg-white rounded-full transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8 text-white dark:text-[#000000]"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#000000] dark:text-white">
            EVENTOS
          </h3>
          <p
            class="text-sm text-[#000000]/70 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed"
          >
            Documento la energía y ambiente de celebraciones especiales.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card: Producto -->
      <div
        class="group p-8 border border-[#000000]/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-xl hover:border-[#000000]/30 dark:hover:border-white/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-4">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center bg-[#000000] dark:bg-white rounded-full transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8 text-white dark:text-[#000000]"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#000000] dark:text-white">
            PRODUCTO
          </h3>
          <p
            class="text-sm text-[#000000]/70 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed"
          >
            Imágenes comerciales que impulsan tu presencia digital.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
